{ () (segments=99 dontdraw) databarexpanded } /bwipp.gs1databarexpandedBadSegments isError

% Minimum barxmult for expanded stacked
{ (\(01\)09521234543213) (barxmult=33 format=expandedstacked dontdraw) databarexpanded } /bwipp.databarStackedOmniBarXmult isError

%
